article:
'Fresh FM' is a Dutch regional, commercial radio station currently transmitted
through air in the regions: Greater Amsterdam, Utrecht, Haaglanden and
Rhine/Haarlemmermeer. Also, it broadcasts for free via the Internet. Fresh FM's
programming is primarily dance music and is very diverse within that genre. The
channel's target is 17 to 49 year olds and is in its broadcast area of the most
listened to regional radio stations. The studio is based in Zoetermeer. Fresh
FM's slogan is "Feel good!" and "It's all about the music".
